headline: Venture Global debut to test appetite for energy IPOs after Trump's policy pivot
summary: Venture Global LNG will debut on public markets on Friday after sharply lowering its IPO valuation to $60.5 billion, but still set to be one of the largest U.S.-listed energy companies. ...
